{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x18,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x49,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Be still my beating heart, what a glorious view... Not bad at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "This underground space...I wonder if it was dug with human power..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I wonder who built this, and for what purpose..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Who knows? This place was only recently discovered, so basically nothing is known about this place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "If it was built on the surface,<CR>it would've made our jobs easier."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I see, so it's more difficult if it's underground?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Of course. There's the constant danger of a cave-in, and we don't want sewage or a hot spring to spout up, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Well, I guess a hot spring wouldn't be that bad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...Anyway, this place is hot, dark, and cramped. There's nothing good about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Just listening to you talk about it...makes it seem like a lot of trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Well, if it was easy, I'd be out of a job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Prospecting... When I think about it, it's a tough occupation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Working with a bunch of guys is tougher."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Whenever something happened, some guys would always touch my butt in the midst of the confusion."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat!? Th-Things like that happened?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Yup, yup. Well, I've given those goons a good piece of my mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "But then, they stopped treating me like a girl..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I mean, isn't there something weird about me being the first girl to be taken out on a slag hunt?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "It is true that I have the most physical strength out of all of them, but still."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh, you have the most...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Jeez, those guys are so unreliable..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Whoa... Regina, you're amazing!<CR>I could never be like you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm. I think you're better off not trying to be like me. Although, it is a fun occupation once you try it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "(Regina works with men, and she's so cool...)"
        }
    ]
}